Class ActionBar.Tab

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.support.v4.app.ActionBar.Tab
  • Enclosing class:
    ActionBar

    public abstract static class ActionBar.Tab
extends java.lang.Object

    A tab in the action bar.

    Tabs manage the hiding and showing of Fragment.
